            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-edd23984-b41e-40a8-afc3-cefce4e1e78f">
                Mr. Churchill  (Woodford)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-edd23984-b41e-40a8-afc3-cefce4e1e78f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
