    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Well, the Government will have an opportunity of speaking. The Home Secretary can say what it is. I am told by people who have studied this and have great professional attainments that what I have just said is correct because the jury will in many cases have to be advised—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
