            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-cb484635-9f4f-4d4d-bdd6-5739f89ae8b0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
