<p class="">Has it occurred to the hon. Gentleman that in the case of a systematic poisoner the would-be victim has a chance to grow suspicious after a few weeks that he or she is being poisoned and can leave home or seek advice? The immediate poisoner gives the victim no chance at all.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0ce9d0bd-4b6c-4c54-9c7d-3a3daee08c22" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
