                Mr. Silverman
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e337fd2f-0b17-4d7a-b1a7-ff57d00ff09c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-07-15/debates/5271a94e-9848-453f-8118-96040481a0f7/Clause1%E2%80%94(SuspensionOfDeathPenaltyForMurder)#contribution-e337fd2f-0b17-4d7a-b1a7-ff57d00ff09c">
