<p class="">That is really the most fantastic argument. The hon. Member is saying that if one accepts a certain <span id="1467" class="column-number" data-column-number="1467"></span> procedure as the right procedure to follow on a particular occasion one is to be bound forever after by the result of adopting that procedure.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
