        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-dff17af7-f015-49e5-bb61-cc4221cffcb9">
                The Minister of Education (Mr. Tomlinson)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dff17af7-f015-49e5-bb61-cc4221cffcb9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
