    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is it not a fact that about 1923 a boy named Jacoby, who was under 18 was executed?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1e57e743-3c0a-4e42-8dec-52a34f6c8ff6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-07-15/debates/5271a94e-9848-453f-8118-96040481a0f7/Clause1%E2%80%94(SuspensionOfDeathPenaltyForMurder)#contribution-1e57e743-3c0a-4e42-8dec-52a34f6c8ff6">
