er, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Taylor, R. J. (Morpeth)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wyatt, W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Rankin, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Taylor, Dr. S. (Barnet)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Yates, V. F.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Rees-Williams, D. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thomas, D. E. (Aberdare)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Young, Sir R. (Newton)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Reeves, J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thomas, George (Cardiff)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Younger, Hon. Kenneth</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Reid, T. (Swindon)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thomas, Ivor (Keighley)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td></td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Rhodes, H.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thomas, I. O. (Wrekin)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>TELLERS FOR THE AYES:</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Ridealgh, Mrs. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thomas, John R. (Dover)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mr. Snow and Mr. G. Wallace</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Robens, A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Thorneycroft, Harry (Clayton)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td></td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division"> </table></p><p class="Division"> <table type="span"></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td colspan="3" align="center"></p><p class="Division">  <b>NOES.</b></p><p class="Division"> </td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Aitken, Hon. Max</td></p><p cl